# Miso-Chile Asparagus With Tofu

Based on [https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1025327-miso-chile-asparagus-with-tofu](https://cooking.nytimes.com/recipes/1025327-miso-chile-asparagus-with-tofu)

